00:37:23,770 --> 00:37:26,890
 To San Ha, So Hui is his second chance. 

416
00:37:26,890 --> 00:37:29,730
 He can try to push her away all he wants. 

417
00:37:29,730 --> 00:37:32,310
 He can't ignore So Hui forever. 

