472
00:42:57,790 --> 00:42:59,340
My friend is your friend, Oppa.

473
00:42:59,340 --> 00:43:02,520
Not true. Ordinary people don't think that way.

474
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:04,280
It's a new place downtown,

475
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:08,140
and it's apparently very famous in Seoul, too.

476
00:43:10,070 --> 00:43:13,200
Dal's mom is making a big gesture by treating us.

477
00:43:13,200 --> 00:43:17,360
The students who've been there said there's no need to chew the meat.

478
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:20,120
When you place it in your mouth, it melts.

479
00:43:20,120 --> 00:43:22,900
It just melts on your tongue.

480
00:43:24,150 --> 00:43:26,190
Nothing is free.

481
00:43:26,190 --> 00:43:28,280
- You're going, right? 
 - Let's go.

482
00:43:28,280 --> 00:43:30,540
So it's just us two?

483
00:43:32,410 --> 00:43:36,310
Then meet me after school in front of the main entrance.

484
00:43:39,050 --> 00:43:40,740
Why is she treating us, though?

485
00:43:40,740 --> 00:43:43,030
Let's hear that first.

486
00:43:44,150 --> 00:43:46,280
To be honest...

487
00:43:52,300 --> 00:43:55,020
 I just... 

488
00:43:55,020 --> 00:43:56,650
 have... 

489
00:43:56,650 --> 00:43:58,870
 a favor to ask him. 

490
00:43:58,870 --> 00:44:01,320
 Your grade in math is three? 
     

491
00:44:02,700 --> 00:44:05,940
 Sure, grades drop sometimes. 

492
00:44:07,660 --> 00:44:09,200
 Rather than getting this result in Grade 12, 

493
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:12,270
 it's better to face it now and be prepared. 

494
00:44:13,070 --> 00:44:14,080
 Okay. 

495
00:44:14,080 --> 00:44:16,210
 Didn't you say you got notes from Joo Won's oppa? 

496
00:44:16,210 --> 00:44:18,290
 Did you get them or not? 

497
00:44:19,680 --> 00:44:20,970
 Not yet. 

498
00:44:20,970 --> 00:44:22,430
 You're too shy. 

499
00:44:22,430 --> 00:44:25,690
 Can't you even ask your friend's brother for a simple favor? 

500
00:44:26,330 --> 00:44:29,440
 I was going to ask when we got closer. 

501
00:44:29,440 --> 00:44:32,000
 Should I meet Joo Won's brother? 

502
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:36,150
 Yes! I'll treat him to something tasty, so tell him to come with Joo Won. 

503
00:44:41,890 --> 00:44:44,510
If that's the case, aren't I the only one invited?

504
00:44:45,470 --> 00:44:48,320
You two don't really need to be here, do you?

505
00:44:48,320 --> 00:44:50,500
I don't know what you're talking about.

506
00:44:50,500 --> 00:44:54,400
Delicious food is even more delicious when you eat it together.

507
00:44:55,930 --> 00:44:58,970
- Welcome. 
 - Welcome!

508
00:45:20,620 --> 00:45:22,330
Have a seat.

509
00:45:29,900 --> 00:45:31,700
CSAT is approaching.

510
00:45:31,700 --> 00:45:33,920
I hope I'm not taking too much of your time.

511
00:45:33,920 --> 00:45:37,210
Oh, you're not.

512
00:45:37,210 --> 00:45:40,190
We should order the 4-person set.

513
00:45:41,800 --> 00:45:45,540
We have two boys here. Order the 6-person set.

514
00:45:45,540 --> 00:45:48,370
Oh, then...

515
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:53,700
What do you want to eat? Is there anything you want to eat?

516
00:45:57,050 --> 00:45:59,320
We've never been to a place like this, so we don't know.

517
00:45:59,320 --> 00:46:01,030
- Right? 
 - Yes.

518
00:46:01,030 --> 00:46:02,670
Have you never tried this in Seoul?

519
00:46:02,670 --> 00:46:05,830
Oh, then the 6-person set–

520
00:46:05,830 --> 00:46:08,490
