524
00:46:18,780 --> 00:46:21,060
- All right? 
 - Yes.

525
00:46:26,680 --> 00:46:28,540
Pardon me.

526
00:46:29,300 --> 00:46:31,230
Enjoy.

527
00:46:38,250 --> 00:46:41,010
Thank you for the food.

528
00:46:41,900 --> 00:46:44,770
